{% assign weeks = "Week 1 <br>
Mindful Munching:Access your new meal plan with tons of new recipes that don’t compromise flavor!
|Week 2<br>
Supplement Savvy:Start adding Curalin to your regime. We’ll guide you through it every step of the way!
|Week 3<br>
Find your Flow:Add in a movement routine that works for YOU! Go at your own pace, from the comfortability of your home. It’s doable, maintainable, and even enjoyable!
|Week 4<br>
Small Steps, Big Wins:Set yourself up for success! Learn the health habits that allow you to maintain what you learned over the 30 days. You’re only just beginning.
" | split: "|" %}

<div class="how-work">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="sub-title">
          How the 30 day challenge works:         
        </div>
        <div class="sub-text">Each week, we’ll conquer a new health habit together!</div>
     
      

      <ul class="list-ic horizontal">
        <li><span>1</span></li>
        <li><span>2</span></li>
        <li><span>3</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="how-work-wrapper">
      {% for week in weeks %}
        <div class="how-work-text">
          <div class="week-title">{{ week | split: ":" | first }}</div>
          <div class="border-bottom-week"></div>
          <div class="week-text">{{ week | split: ":" | last }}</div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
      
    </div>
</div>
